track_notes: Nice place to be! sometime there are sheep with dog but no fear they are fine! Plenty room for antenna and no problems for parking. Nice panorama
Small walk up to the summit, in summertime get some water. Plenty room for setup antenna

A 3 hours walk (up and down) on a nice path, it is not hard walk; you can park at Plan du Var next to the railway station and look for the starting point in middle of grass, then you will found yellow marks all the way. Plenty room on summit with 2 wooden tables. Nice landscape all around.
easy summit, walking on the road
you can park (one car) and found the path in between two houses. Short and easy, plenty room on summit
